      "wikitext": "<div id=\"infoboxborder\" style=\"float:right;display:block;\">\n{|\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''Coop'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''Big Coop'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''Deluxe Coop'''\n|-\n|\n![[File:Coop.png|96px]]\n![[File:Big Coop.png|96px]]\n![[File:Deluxe Coop.png|96px]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|Information\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Upgrades From\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|N/A\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|Coop\n|Big Coop\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Building Cost\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Price|4000}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Price|10000}}\n|{{Price|20000}}\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Building Materials\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|Wood|300}}{{Name|Stone|100}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|Wood|400}}{{Name|Stone|150}}\n|{{Name|Wood|500}}{{Name|Stone|200}}\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Capacity\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|4\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|8\n|12\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Animals\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|White Chicken|link=Chicken}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|White Chicken|link=Chicken}}{{Name|Duck}}{{Name|Void Chicken}}{{Name|Dinosaur}}{{Name|Golden Chicken}}\n|{{Name|White Chicken|link=Chicken}}{{Name|Duck}}{{Name|Void Chicken}}{{Name|Dinosaur}}{{Name|Golden Chicken}}{{Name|Rabbit}}\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Footprint\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|'''6x3'''<br />[[File:Marker3x6.png]]\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|'''6x3'''<br />[[File:Marker3x6.png]]\n|'''6x3'''<br />[[File:Marker3x6.png]]\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Features\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|\n* [[Hay Hopper]]\n* Feeding Bench\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|\n* [[Hay Hopper]]\n* Feeding Bench\n* [[Incubator]]\n|\n* [[Hay Hopper]]\n* Feeding Bench\n* [[Incubator]]\n* Autofeed System\n|}</div>\n\nThe '''Coop''' is a type of [[Carpenter's Shop#Farm Buildings|farm building]] purchasable and upgradable from [[Robin]] at the [[Carpenter's Shop]].\n\n==Construction==\nThe Coop takes three days to construct. During this time, [[Robin]] is unreachable for [[Friendship|dialogue or gifting]].\n\nUpgrading the Coop requires two days. During this time, the coop can be used as normal. Robin can be found inside the Coop for purposes such as [[Friendship|dialogue or gifting]].\n\nThe total cost of a Deluxe Coop, built from scratch, is {{Price|34000}}, {{Name|Wood|1200|class=inline}} and {{Name|Stone|450|class=inline}} (Or, if all wood and stone are bought from Robin during Year 1, {{Price|55000}}, and {{Price|139000}} if bought in Year 2+.)\n\nIf the player chooses the [[Farm Maps#Meadowlands|Meadowlands Farm Map]], there will be a coop built on their farm to start.\n\n==Features==\nThe coop can house [[chicken]]s, [[duck]]s, [[rabbit]]s, and [[dinosaur]]s. Once you have unlocked an animal by building the coop needed to house it, that animal can be placed in any other non-upgraded coops you have built as well.\n\nThe Deluxe Coop features an Autofeed System; [[hay]] from your [[silo]]s will be automatically distributed. (You can still let the animals feed on [[grass]] outside, and the hay will not be eaten.)\n\nCoop Animals may be stuck outside at night if the coop doors are closed. The conditions for this are not clear (see [[Animals#Animals Trapped Outside|Animals trapped outside]]). If an animal is stuck outside the coop at night, the next day their mood will be \"grumpy\". Animals stuck outside are also subject to [[Animals#Wild Animal Attacks|Wild Animal Attacks]].\n\nThe Coop can also be used in a manner similar to the [[Shed]] for storing [[Chest|Chests]], [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]], [[Furniture]], etc. The animals are undisturbed by the clutter, even if their paths are blocked. However, excessive obstructions may prevent the spawning of [[:Category:Animal Products|coop animal products]].\n\n<gallery>\nAnimal left outside dialog.png\n</gallery>\n\n==Interior==\n<gallery>\nChickens fed.png|Coop Interior\nBig Coop Interior.png|Big Coop Interior\nDeluxe Coop Interior.png|Deluxe Coop Interior\n</gallery>\n\n{{NavboxBuildings}}\n\n[[Category:Farm buildings]]\n\n[[de:Hühnerstall]]\n[[es:Corral]]\n[[fr:Poulailler]]\n[[it:Stia]]\n[[ja:小屋]]\n[[ko:닭장]]\n[[hu:Csűr]]\n[[pt:Galinheiro]]\n[[ru:Птичник]]\n[[tr:Kümes]]\n[[zh:鸡舍]]"
    }
